staxel.village.dialogue.PrincePrimary.li: Good day, local citizen!
Aha! That distinctive attire!
Would you happen to be the local patissier?
Nod mutely
Shake head
Ah, well that is quite the surprise...
Could you direct me to them perchance?
Excellent! It was my greatest desire to meet you in person!
Though...I must admit, you don't quite have the...aura I expected...
But nevertheless! I had heard from my wife-to-be that your skills are said to be unparalleled!
This document I had my staff produce outlines the design for a magnificent ^c:1486b0;wedding gift^c:pop;.
Very...'islandish' you might say.
Please exercise your considerable skills and bring this to me at your earliest convenience!
Is that...? No. That does not quite look like the designs I provided...
Please do get back to me with the ^c:1486b0;wedding gift^c:pop; at your earliest convenience!
Ah! I recognise the object you bear!
This seems...adequate.
No. That is not quite the word I sought...
Fantastic! That was it! Fantastic!
Ah! But I must provide you with a suitable reward...
I'm led to believe that is how these things work...
Perhaps this will do? Merely a small token of my appreciation!
Now I must return to my betrothed to prepare for the wedding!
Good day, local citizen!
I'm seeking a patissier of some renown who is purportedly based on this island...
Would you happen to be able to direct me to them?
I shall endeavour to be more careful...
Ah, you were the patissier from before, no?
Can you believe she was so averse to the wonderful ^c:1486b0;wedding gift^c:pop; you created?
Such audacity! Ungratefulness! Who could have imagined a political marriage could turn out so wrong?
I have written up a letter outlining my feelings on the matter. Please deliver it to her post-haste.
Ah! A ^c:1486b0;letter^c:pop; for me?
...how profound! How wonderfully eloquent! Only an angel could have written with such grace!
Perhaps...perhaps I was mistaken...
I shall seek her out once more myself!
Take this as a token of my gratitude!
NO!
Ah! Of course! You are quite right...
It was a fine ^c:1486b0;wedding gift^c:pop;..
